SOURCE: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/compiler/rustc_error_codes/src/error_codes/E0501.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: Rust
CODE:
```
```
fn inside_closure(x: &mut i32) {}
fn outside_closure(x: &mut i32) {}

fn foo(a: &mut i32) {
    let mut bar = |s: &mut i32| {
        inside_closure(s)
    };
    outside_closure(a);
    bar(a);
}
```
```

