SOURCE: https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/compiler/rustc_error_codes/src/error_codes/E0264.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
```
#![feature(lang_items)]
#![allow(internal_features)]

extern "C" {
    #[lang = "cake"] // error: unknown external lang item: `cake`
    fn cake();
}
```

